<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/809677-i-cannot-get-over-the-high-diplomatic">I cannot get over the high diplomatic thriller in this book. Can anyone suggest any other book with similar storyline?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_809677'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F119389.Windmills_of_the_Gods">like</a></span>

