<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/32987612-chandni"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1595529791i/32987612._UY100_CR16,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/32987612-chandni">Chandni</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Best Laid Plans by this author, Deception Point by Dan Brown<br/>Brown’s chapters are fast-paced, well-researched, and short (~3 pages on average). Happy r<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Best Laid Plans by this author, Deception Point by Dan Brown<br />Brown’s chapters are fast-paced, well-researched, and short (~3 pages on average). Happy reading!!<br /><a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
