<div id="review_1901995739" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1901995739" />
    <a title="Bren fall in love with the sea." class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/61659069-bren-fall-in-love-with-the-sea"><img alt="Bren fall in love with the sea." src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1625977334p2/61659069.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1901995739?book_show_action=true">Feb 03, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Bren fall in love with the sea." class="user" itemprop="url" name="Bren fall in love with the sea." href="/user/show/61659069-bren-fall-in-love-with-the-sea">Bren fall in love with the sea.</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780446350105" href="/book/show/580281.Windmills_of_the_Gods">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/61659069-bren-fall-in-love-with-the-sea?shelf=political-fiction">political-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/61659069-bren-fall-in-love-with-the-sea?shelf=want-to-read-a-second-time">want-to-read-a-second-time</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/61659069-bren-fall-in-love-with-the-sea?shelf=mystery">mystery</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/61659069-bren-fall-in-love-with-the-sea?shelf=crime">crime</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/61659069-bren-fall-in-love-with-the-sea?shelf=dark-and-heavy">dark-and-heavy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/61659069-bren-fall-in-love-with-the-sea?shelf=read-and-reviewed">read-and-reviewed</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/61659069-bren-fall-in-love-with-the-sea?shelf=spies">spies</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/61659069-bren-fall-in-love-with-the-sea?shelf=suspense">suspense</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/61659069-bren-fall-in-love-with-the-sea?shelf=thriller-horror">thriller-horror</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1901995739" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6553754663755053605">“Even when lightning flashes inside them [clouds], we say they are only clouds and turn our attention to the next meal, next pain, next breath, the next page. This is how we go on.” <br/>― Sidney Sheldon, Windmills of the Gods<br/><br/><br/><br/><br/>Another good Sheldon book. This one combines politics with plenty of mystery and intrigue and is an engrossing well written book.<br/><br/>In spite of my love for all things Sheldon, this one, for me, was not quite as good, as some of his others. There are though plenty of Windmill lovers</span>
  <span id="freeText6553754663755053605" style="display:none">“Even when lightning flashes inside them [clouds], we say they are only clouds and turn our attention to the next meal, next pain, next breath, the next page. This is how we go on.” <br />― Sidney Sheldon, Windmills of the Gods<br /><br /><br /><br /><br />Another good Sheldon book. This one combines politics with plenty of mystery and intrigue and is an engrossing well written book.<br /><br />In spite of my love for all things Sheldon, this one, for me, was not quite as good, as some of his others. There are though plenty of Windmill lovers who would say different! I have read some of the reviews on this book and I remember it as a best seller.<br /><br />I have other favorite Sheldon books but this one is still a great quick read an d one that I have read a few times now. It is still complex with the signature Sheldon twist and plenty of twists and turns.</span>
  <a data-text-id="6553754663755053605" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


